title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, East Woods]
description: The underbrush is quite thick at the edges of the trail.  Dim moonlight filters down through the leafy boughs above, picking out a small shadowed path that maneuvers its way around the trunks of the trees like a dusty serpent slithering through a maze.

The underbrush is quite thick at the edges of the trail.  Speckled motes of sunlight dance down through the leafy boughs above.  A small path maneuvers its way around the trunks of the trees like a dusty serpent slithering through a maze.
